parameters: \n<Detective>No good... It's locked and won't open...

\n<sine:ω>ω: Kishishishi! Welcome to the room of the genius
gamer, Sine:ω-sama!

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Sigh... This is why ignorant people
are... not knowing the genius gamer Sine:ω-sama...

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]You're one of those people who still go
to the library to do research, aren't you?

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]So, you're the type of person who proudly
shares outdated information from decades ago and
annoys everyone around you, huh?

\n<Detective>You're quite cheeky... Hey, tell me how to get out
of here.

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Haah... You're so lacking in
comprehension it's pathetic... There's no way I'm
going to tell you, idiot. Use your brain and think
about the situation, dumbass.

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]There's a door on the monitor, and the
door is locked. It's obvious that I, the one
behind the monitor, have complete control over
where to go and how to proceed, unlike you
clueless old man.
\n<Detective>...So, what is it that you want me to do?

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]This is a stage prepared by the genius
gamer me, you know? It's obviously a game, you
idiot. It's true that the government's dogs are
all incompetent, huh?

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]If you know your enemy and know yourself,
you will not be defeated in a hundred battles.

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]When I heard about you from Luna-neechan,
I obviously did my research and found out
everything about you, lol.
CocoStageMoniter_06_おっさんのプロフィール

\n<sine:ω>Detective, you're a Deputy Inspector from the
Metropolitan Police Department's Investigation
Support and Analysis Division, right? You were
dispatched to investigate the case of someone
going insane, correct?

\n<Detective>No way... Hacking? Ridiculous... Something like
that from a child...

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Please don't compare me to a stupid brat
like the bitch in the previous room, okay?

\n<sine:ω>My IQ is 145, so I can easily break through the
defenses made by lowlifes like you, even right
after waking up. \C[24]
\n<Detective>What the hell... This is a crime!

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Huh? I don't want to hear it from you,
lol. You must have slept with that bitch, right?

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]There's no point in hiding, you know?
Cameras are installed all over this train, lol.

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Look, there's even a video of you and the
bitch's actions...

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]A-anyway! You understand now, right? I
have your information and weaknesses in my grasp!

\n<Detective>(...Footage from the in-car camera...? Could this
be...?)

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Kishishishi! Now, for the game I want you
to play, first answer this quiz for me!

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]According to your answer, the door will
open, so proceed through the dungeon beyond...
\n<Detective>...Hey, you, the quiz isn't being displayed...

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Huh?! What? Oh, it's true, the link to
the shared screen is disconnected...

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]W-Wait... My real face is dangerous...
C-Cancel command...!
\n<Detective>...Do I just need to enter this room?

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Hey...! Ah! No! That's the correct...
no... ah...

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]Y-Y-Yikes...! That... that room is
dangerous! You'll die if you enter that room, you
know!

\n<Detective>...I understand, I understand. So, which room is
the correct one?

\n<sine:ω>ω: \C[24]\{Right!!\} The right door! Or the second
one from the left... Just not the one in the
middle...!

\n<Detective>Just wait there, Coco-chan. There are a few things
I need to ask you too.
